        public void updateGeofence(GeofenceLocation existingGeofence,
                           GeofenceLocation geofence)
        This method deletes an existing geofence and adds the new geofence. As there is no direct update method provided by GeofencingApi we have to first delete and then add it method on the geofence
        参数:
        existingGeofence - existing geofence
        geofence - new geofencelocation
